---
const whatsappLink = "https://wa.me/51934809665"; 
---

<section
  id="cuidado"
  class="relative overflow-hidden px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-primary/5"
>
  <!-- Elementos decorativos de fondo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -top-32 -left-32 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse-slow"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-32 -right-32 w-96 h-96 bg-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-float-slow"></div>
    
    <!-- Patrones florales sutiles -->
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-10 opacity-[0.03] rotate-45">
      <i class="fas fa-spa text-7xl text-primary"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-10 opacity-[0.03] -rotate-12">
      <i class="fas fa-leaf text-6xl text-primary"></i>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Header con animación -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20 animate-fade-in-up">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-primary/50"></span>
        <span class="text-primary font-medium tracking-wider text-sm uppercase">Cuidado Premium</span>
        <span class="w-12 h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-primary/50"></span>
      </div>
      
      <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-primary mb-6">
        <span class="block mb-2">Guía de Cuidado</span>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary">
          para tus Flores
        </span>
      </h2>
      
      <p class="text-secondary/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Sigue estos consejos expertos para que la belleza de Ginevra te acompañe por más tiempo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pasos con timeline -->
    <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Línea vertical decorativa -->
      <div class="absolute left-6 lg:left-1/2 transform lg:-translate-x-1/2 h-full w-0.5 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/20 via-primary/10 to-transparent hidden lg:block"></div>

      <!-- Paso 1 -->
      <div class="relative mb-16 lg:mb-20 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12 lg:text-right">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4 lg:mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold text-lg">
              01
            </span>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-primary mb-4">
            <span class="text-secondary/60 font-normal">Paso 1 ·</span> Lugar Ideal
          </h3>
          
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 shadow-sm">
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-secondary/90 leading-relaxed">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-sun text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Fresco y sombra:</strong> Mantén tus flores en un lugar fresco,
                  lejos de la luz directa del sol, corrientes de aire fuertes o fuentes de calor.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-apple-alt text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Lejos de la fruta:</strong> No coloques las flores cerca de frutas
                  maduras, ya que emiten gas etileno y aceleran el marchitamiento.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Imagen Paso 1 -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute -inset-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl transform rotate-3 animate-rotate-slow"></div>
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-500">
              <img
                src="/cuidado-lugar-ideal.webp"
                alt="Flores en un lugar fresco y sombreado"
                class="w-full h-64 lg:h-80 object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 2 -->
      <div class="relative mb-16 lg:mb-20 lg:flex lg:flex-row-reverse lg:items-center lg:gap-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4 lg:mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold text-lg">
              02
            </span>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-primary mb-4">
            <span class="text-secondary/60 font-normal">Paso 2 ·</span> Alimento para Flores
          </h3>
          
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 shadow-sm">
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-secondary/90 leading-relaxed">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-flask text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Preparación:</strong> Mezcla el sobre de alimento en un litro de
                  agua tibia o a temperatura ambiente para una mejor disolución.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-tint text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Dosificación:</strong> Usa la mezcla según el tamaño del florero.
                  Puedes guardar el sobrante en una botella cerrada.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Imagen Paso 2 -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute -inset-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl transform -rotate-3 animate-rotate-slow"></div>
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-500">
              <img
                src="/cuidado-alimento.webp"
                alt="Alimento para flores y preparación"
                class="w-full h-64 lg:h-80 object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Nutrición floral</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 3 -->
      <div class="relative mb-16 lg:mb-20 lg:flex lg:items-center lg:gap-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-12 lg:text-right">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4 lg:mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold text-lg">
              03
            </span>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-primary mb-4">
            <span class="text-secondary/60 font-normal">Paso 3 ·</span> Para Ramos
          </h3>
          
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 shadow-sm">
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-secondary/90 leading-relaxed">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-cut text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Corte de tallos:</strong> Corta aproximadamente 2 cm en un ángulo
                  de 45° antes de colocarlos en el florero.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-leaf text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Limpieza del agua:</strong> Retira hojas sumergidas para evitar
                  bacterias.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-sync-alt text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Cambio de agua:</strong> Renueva el agua cada 2 días y lava el
                  florero.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Imagen Paso 3 -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute -inset-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl transform rotate-3 animate-rotate-slow"></div>
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-500">
              <img
                src="/cuidado-ramos.webp"
                alt="Cuidado de ramos florales"
                class="w-full h-64 lg:h-80 object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Cada 2 días</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Paso 4 -->
      <div class="relative lg:flex lg:flex-row-reverse lg:items-center lg:gap-12 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.4s">
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pl-12">
          <div class="inline-block mb-4 lg:mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary font-semibold text-lg">
              04
            </span>
          </div>
          
          <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl lg:text-3xl text-primary mb-4">
            <span class="text-secondary/60 font-normal">Paso 4 ·</span> Para Arreglos
          </h3>
          
          <div class="bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-primary/10 shadow-sm">
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-secondary/90 leading-relaxed">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-tint text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Hidratación:</strong> Agrega media taza de agua fresca diariamente
                  al centro del arreglo para mantener la espuma húmeda.
                </span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <i class="fas fa-ban text-primary/70 mt-1"></i>
                <span>
                  <strong class="text-primary">Sin trasplante:</strong> No es necesario retirar las flores de la
                  espuma; están diseñadas para permanecer ahí.
                </span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Imagen Paso 4 -->
        <div class="lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="relative group">
            <div class="absolute -inset-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-transparent rounded-3xl transform -rotate-3 animate-rotate-slow"></div>
            <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg group-hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-500">
              <img
                src="/cuidado-arreglos.webp"
                alt="Cuidado de arreglos florales"
                class="w-full h-64 lg:h-80 object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700"
                loading="lazy"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/20 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg px-3 py-1">
                <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Hidratación diaria</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Final -->
    <div class="text-center mt-16 lg:mt-20 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.5s">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/5 to-secondary/5 rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-10 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary/10">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6">
          <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
            <h4 class="font-serif text-xl lg:text-2xl text-primary mb-2">
              ¿Necesitas más consejos personalizados?
            </h4>
            <p class="text-secondary/80">
              Nuestro equipo de expertos puede asesorarte sobre el cuidado específico de cada flor.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href={whatsappLink}
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="group/cta relative bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-primary/25 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 whitespace-nowrap"
          >
            <span class="relative z-10 flex items-center gap-3">
              <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
              <span>Consultar con expertos</span>
            </span>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-secondary to-primary rounded-full opacity-0 group-hover/cta:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300"></div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Animaciones personalizadas */
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes rotateSlow {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: rotate(3deg);
    }
    50% {
      transform: rotate(5deg);
    }
  }

  /* Clases de animación */
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulseSlow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .animate-float-slow {
    animation: floatSlow 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .animate-rotate-slow {
    animation: rotateSlow 10s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }

  /* Animaciones reutilizadas */
  @keyframes pulseSlow {
    0%, 100% {
      opacity: 0.05;
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes floatSlow {
    0%, 100% {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
    }
  }

  /* Efectos de hover */
  .group:hover .group-hover\:scale-105 {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  /* Transiciones suaves */
  .transition-all {
    transition-property: all;
    transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .transition-transform {
    transition-property: transform;
    transition-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  /* Responsive improvements */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .lg\:flex-row-reverse {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    .lg\:text-right {
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .lg\:pr-12, .lg\:pl-12 {
      padding-right: 0;
      padding-left: 0;
    }
  }
</style>